[{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"CurrentModule = QMOC","category":"page"},{"location":"#QMOC","page":"Home","title":"QMOC","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Documentation for QMOC.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Modules = [QMOC]\nOrder   = [:function, :type]","category":"page"},{"location":"#Base.hash-Tuple{Trajectory}","page":"Home","title":"Base.hash","text":"hash(trajectory::Trajectory) -> UInt\n\nReturns a hash of the trajectory properties.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.adoptedTrajectories-Tuple{}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.adoptedTrajectories","text":"adoptedTrajectories()\n\nReturns a vector of all trajectory hashes in the filesystem that are in the metadata.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.allTrajectories-Tuple{}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.allTrajectories","text":"allTrajectories()\n\nReturns a vector of all trajectory hashes in the filesystem.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.archive-Tuple{Simulation}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.archive","text":"archive(sim::Simulation) :: Nothing\n\nArchives all trajectories in a simulation.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.archive-Tuple{Trajectory}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.archive","text":"archive(traj::Trajectory) :: Nothing\n\nArchives a trajectory by first checking if it is complete and then archiving it.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.archivedTrajectories-Tuple{}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.archivedTrajectories","text":"archivedTrajectories()\n\nReturns a vector of all trajectory hashes in the archive.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.backup-Tuple{}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.backup","text":"backup()\n\nBacks up all metadata and measurements (including the archive) to a folder called \"backup\" in the data folder.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.boolArchived-Tuple{Simulation}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.boolArchived","text":"boolArchived(sim::Simulation) :: Bool\n\nChecks if a simulation is archived, i.e. if all trajectories are archived.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.boolArchived-Tuple{Trajectory}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.boolArchived","text":"boolArchived(traj::Trajectory) :: Bool\n\nChecks if a trajectory is archived, i.e. if the measurement average is present in the archive.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.boolComplete-Tuple{Simulation}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.boolComplete","text":"boolComplete(sim::Simulation) :: Bool\n\nChecks if a simulation is complete, i.e. if all linked trajectories are complete.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.boolComplete-Tuple{Trajectory}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.boolComplete","text":"boolComplete(traj::Trajectory) :: Bool\n\nChecks if a trajectory is complete, i.e. if all measurements are present. Automatically averages if all measurements are present but no average is found.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.cleanup-Tuple{}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.cleanup","text":"cleanup()\n\nCleans up the filesystem by archiving all trajectories in the metadata and deleting all orphaned trajectories.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.countTrajectories-Tuple{Simulation}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.countTrajectories","text":"countTrajectories(sim::Simulation) :: Int\n\nCounts the number of trajectories in a simulation.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.loadMetadata-Tuple{String}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.loadMetadata","text":"loadMetadata(name::String)\n\nLoads the metadata of a simulation from the filesystem and returns it. If the simulation name cannot be matched, it loads all metadata.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.loadMetadata-Tuple{}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.loadMetadata","text":"loadMetadata()\n\nLoads all metadata from the filesystem and returns a vector of simulations.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.missingTrajectories-Tuple{Simulation}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.missingTrajectories","text":"missingTrajectories(simulation::Simulation)\n\nReturns a vector of all trajectories in a simulation that are not complete.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.orphanedTrajectories-Tuple{}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.orphanedTrajectories","text":"orphanedMeasurements()\n\nReturns a vector of all trajectory hashes in the filesystem that are not in the metadata.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.parameter_circle-Tuple{Any}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.parameter_circle","text":"parameter_circle(radius)\n\nReturns the cartesian coordinates of a circle with radius `radius` around the isometric point.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.parameter_distance-Tuple{Any}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.parameter_distance","text":"parameter_distance(param)\n\nReturns the distance of a parameter set (px, py, pz) from the isotropic point in the parameter space.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.parameter_full-Tuple{Any}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.parameter_full","text":"parameter_full(resolution)\n\nReturns a list of rational parameter sets (px, py, pz) filling the whole parameter space.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.parameter_line-Tuple{Any, Any, Any}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.parameter_line","text":"parameter_line(pointA, pointB, steps)\n\nReturns a list of rational parameter sets (px, py, pz) on a line between pointA and pointB with steps number of points.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.parameter_wedge","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.parameter_wedge","text":"parameter_wedge(resolution, mode=:radial)\n\nReturns a list of rational parameter sets (px, py, pz) filling the wedge between the isotropic point and the px=1 point, px=py point. Mode can be either :radial or :linear.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#QMOC.parametric_to_cartesian-Tuple{Any}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.parametric_to_cartesian","text":"parametric_to_cartesian(params)\n\nReturns the cartesian coordinates of a parameter set (px, py, pz).\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.readTrajectory-Tuple{Trajectory}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.readTrajectory","text":"readTrajectory(traj::Trajectory) :: Measurement\n\nReads a trajectory from the archive or from the filesystem. Assumes that the trajectory is complete.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.removeTrajectories-Tuple{Simulation}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.removeTrajectories","text":"removeTrajectories(sim::Simulation) :: Nothing\n\nRemoves all trajectories in a simulation from the filesystem.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.standard_lines-Tuple{Any}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.standard_lines","text":"standard_lines(resolution)\n\nReturns a list of rational parameter sets (px, py, pz) on the two lines between the isotropic point and the px=1 point, px=py point.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.writeAverage-Tuple{Trajectory}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.writeAverage","text":"writeAverage(traj::Trajectory) :: nothing\n\nOverwrites a trajectory file containing a measurement series with its average.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#QMOC.writeMetadata-Tuple{Simulation}","page":"Home","title":"QMOC.writeMetadata","text":"writeMetadata(sim::Simulation) :: Nothing\n\nWrites the metadata of a simulation to the filesystem.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"}]
